net.jxta.edutella.util
Class RdfUtilities

java.lang.Object
  net.jxta.edutella.util.RdfUtilities

public abstract class RdfUtilities
extends java.lang.Object

RDF Utilities are helping with handling searching and modification of Jena-Framework RDF models, resources, nodes and literals.

See the License, ReadMe.

Depends on edutella-eqm for vocabulary, log4j and jena.

Version:
$Revision: 1.1 $ $Date: 2006/09/20 15:25:11 $
Author:
Wolf Siberski, $Author: jldecoi $
See Also:
